UserData

import model:System as sys
import model:SimpleChat as chat

model:SimpleChat$Model model:User$SimpleChatModel
  extern model:System$RootContext$External$Name = "Simple Chat"
  extern model:System$Model$External$Description = "A (very) simple chat application."
  extern model:System$Model$External$Url = "http://127.0.0.1:5984/repository/model:SimpleChat"
  extern $ModelIdentification = "model:SimpleChat"
  model:System$Model$IndexedContext =>
    model:SimpleChat$ChatApp model:User$MyChatApp
      extern model:System$RootContext$External$Name = "Simple Chat"
      $Chatter -> model:System$Me
    model:System$Model$IndexedContext$Name = "SimpleChat$MyChats"
